Text:
Miss India 2013 is okay. Lekin mera ek sawal hai sab Indian se. Yuvraj Singh ko judge kyon banaya. Aur agar banaya to Sachin ko kyon nahi banaya.

Ye Yuvraj aur Sreesanth dono har jagah kyon ghuse chale jate hai. Cricket khel rahe ho to cricket tak hi simit raho. Inke 'balls' kuch jaida bade ho gaye hai, har jagah pile rehte hai.

Anyway thanks.

Miss India 2013 - Navneet Kaur Dhillion AGE-20 from Chandigarh

11:02 Introduction

29:39 Bikini Round
Bikini Round mein judge ne aisa kya dekha ki isko pass karke top 10 me dal diya.

52:28 Question 1
Ghoda daudana chahti hai.

1:21:27 Question 2
Bechari gribo ke liye kuch karna chahti hai (old ghisa pita repeat answer).

Behenchod cricket match to fix hote hi the, ab Miss India contest bhi fix hone lage hain.
